	- Metin yükleme (PDF/paste)
	- Kelime seçme
	- Sözlük
	- Flashcard (tekrar sistemi)
	- B2B özellikleri
	
	## Başarı Kriteri
	- Kodlama bilmeyen biri kullanabilmeli
	- Mobil uyumlu
	- Hızlı
	- Hatasız
	
	## Tech Stack
	- Next.js 14 (App Router)
	- TypeScript (strict mode)
	- Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
	- PostgreSQL + Prisma ORM
	- Supabase (Auth + Storage)
	
	## Code Standards
	- Functional components only (no class components)
	- Server Actions for mutations
	- Client Components only when necessary (use 'use client' sparingly)
	- Accessibility: WCAG 2.1 AA minimum
	- Error boundaries on all major routes
	
	## Naming Conventions
	- Components: PascalCase (ReaderView.tsx)
	- Utilities: camelCase (formatPageNumber.ts)
	- Database tables: snake_case (reading_sessions)
	
	## Performance
	- Lazy load heavy components
	- Optimize images (next/image)
	- Minimize client-side JavaScript
	
	## Security
	- Never expose API keys in client code
	- Validate all inputs (Zod schemas)
	- Use Supabase RLS for data access
	
	## AI Usage
	- RAG: always cite sources (page/section)
	- Set confidence threshold (0.7 minimum)
	- Cache embeddings (never re-embed same text)
